OL,6,FOne of the biggest unions representing
OL,7,Fsteelworkers is expected to announce
OL,8,Fif strike action will go ahead at the
OL,9,Fplant, in Port Talbot.
OL,11,FThe says that plans to close the
OL,12,Fsteelworks' two blast furnaces, which
OL,13,Fwill , were "incomprehensible".
OL,15,FIt opened balloting for industrial
OL,16,Faction 1 March, urging its 1,500
OL,17,Fmembers to "vote yes for action".
OL,19,FHowever, the Indian conglomerate has
OL,20,Fits 'favourable redundancy package' if
OL,21,Fsteelworkers walk out.
