OL,3,CSteel union to announce if strike
OL,4,Caction will go ahead in Port Talbot
OL,6,FThe ballot result from Unite is
OL,7,Fexpected on Thursday afternoon, 11
OL,8,FApril. It will be the first result of
OL,9,Fthree main union ballots.
OL,11,FThe Community Union will open a ballot
OL,12,Fto its members on Thursday, 11. The
OL,13,FGMB union started its ballot on 4
OL,14,FApril.
OL,16,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,17,Fsaid: "Tata is planning to deal an
OL,18,Fabsolutely devastating blow to Port
OL,19,FTalbot and Llanwern that will spread
OL,20,Fdestruction across the Welsh economy
OL,21,Fand risk national security.
