OL,6,F"Now is the time for the steelworkers
OL,7,Fof Port Talbot and Llanwern to fight
OL,8,Ffor their communities and vote yes to
OL,9,Findustrial action."
OL,11,FHowever, Tata Steel argue that their
OL,12,Fdecision to make redundancies is vital
OL,13,Fto keeping the business afloat and
OL,14,Ftransitioning to a greener way of
OL,15,Fworking.
